{"word":"ἀνελεύθερος","slug":"ἀνελεύθερος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀνελεύθερος</b></el> <p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>not fit for a free man</i>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Aristotle'>Arist.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>illiberal, servile</i>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>3. </b>in money matters, <i>niggardly, stingy</i>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:Adverb'>adv.</a> <el>-ρως</el>, <i>meanly</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}